{"tid":2412372,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"營多撈麵｜解構食上癮之謎香港版原來較多鹽 港人印傭齊試奇怪食法分享癡線回憶","createTime":"2021-02-18T03:56:40.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-23T06:35:11.000Z","uid":130626,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"738557454e606f0e7483439864a6691a183ddafe","tid":2412372,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T03:56:40.000Z","msg":"1月27日「Indomie之母」Nunuk Nuraini逝世，雖然大部份人都未必知她是誰，但她所創的營多撈麵，卻是無數香港人的童年青春回憶，更是無數莘莘學子窮書生的精神兼肉體重要食糧。所以作為「Indomie之母」，絕對配得上「偉人」的稱號，真係要唱返句「營多麼需要你」。今日就讓我們說說有關營多的各大小事兼秘聞。<br />\n<br />\n營多回憶錄 食到入醫院一個暑假肥十幾磅<br />\n營多是不少年輕一代讀書時代的集體回憶，至於是小學、中學定大學呢？就睇閣下年紀有多大同遭遇喇。而營多其實在90年代已引入香港，起初主力在大學以低價格力推，不少大學生更稱之為「低調麵」，至於係「低調」定「抵X」呢，就自己諗喇。講到有關營多的回憶，相信很多人隨隨便便都總會分享到一啲。好似今次問幾位較年輕的同事，都即時講到幾句。Amy：「話說在大學裏有一位同學十分喜歡吃營多撈麵 ，結果吃到胃潰瘍進了醫院，但我們知道後仍是繼續吃，哈哈哈。」Sam：「小學五年級的暑假開始接觸營多撈麵，吃了第一次後便停不下來，整個暑假最少每天吃一個，結果一個暑假肥了近廿磅，班主任認唔到我，之後阿媽就唔畀我食，仲要我減肥。」Dom：「小學小息時必食，我哋叫佢『臭撈』，因為食完個口好臭好勁蒜味！」你又對營多有咩回憶呢？如果真係一句都冇，Sorry，一係你就係上咗年紀，一係你可能在當時同時代脫節囉。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/lifestyle/20210218/WO5W3N6WH5H7PIQIJLAZO52IWI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2F20210218%2FWO5W3N6WH5H7PIQIJLAZO52IWI%2F&d=3nH4Hj8OzEJ%2Fsn4LiTBSOhVENBC9VnKGSHAjWoGsWeM%3D&h=ad67b8d0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2F20210218%2FWO5W3N6WH5H7PIQIJLAZO52IWI%2F&h=9a31a8c7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/lifestyle/20210218/WO5W3N6WH5H7PIQIJLAZO52IWI/</a>"},{"pid":"d22b564dc9f7b5d67f0338881fd7188db104fc7b","tid":2412372,"uid":330227,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T05:17:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/nope.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/nope.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/nope.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n細個嗰陣啲無良小食店一個麵餅開兩個賣"},{"pid":"bf0fc82f713878ee6b483d3e662d42f4872b160a","tid":2412372,"uid":26106,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T05:20:22.000Z","msg":"試過一次過食三個之後<br />\n個種防腐劑既感覺印左係腦入面<br />\n之後聞親浸味都反胃"},{"pid":"5736017ad06f0804682711cb43bfd05cc488d674","tid":2412372,"uid":290118,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T05:21:37.000Z","msg":"話說在大學裏有一位同學十分喜歡吃營多撈麵 ，結果吃到胃潰瘍進了醫院，但我們知道後仍是繼續吃，哈哈哈。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n哈哈哈<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a52d03c3a9516be577540dacdbdb0017a132a2d","tid":2412372,"uid":187676,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"d22b564dc9f7b5d67f0338881fd7188db104fc7b","tid":2412372,"uid":330227,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T05:17:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/nope.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/nope.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/nope.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n細個嗰陣啲無良小食店一個麵餅開兩個賣"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T05:24:29.000Z","msg":"搣開一半叫細撈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n完整一個叫大撈<br />\n跟著一個賣你10蚊，再賣埋野飲，好搵過ibank"},{"pid":"3aab6b58ec3c0ff8e764eeed718326d84ab73693","tid":2412372,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8a52d03c3a9516be577540dacdbdb0017a132a2d","tid":2412372,"uid":187676,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"d22b564dc9f7b5d67f0338881fd7188db104fc7b","tid":2412372,"uid":330227,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T05:17:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/nope.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/nope.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/nope.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n細個嗰陣啲無良小食店一個麵餅開兩個賣"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T05:24:29.000Z","msg":"搣開一半叫細撈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n完整一個叫大撈<br />\n跟著一個賣你10蚊，再賣埋野飲，好搵過ibank"},"cit